9b:["$","p","87",{"className":"mb-4 text-base text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed sm:leading-8","children":["Reducing checkout wait times is one of the highest-impact improvements a retailer can make. Every minute saved translates to happier customers, more sales, and better reviews."]}]
9c:["$","p","88",{"className":"mb-4 text-base text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed sm:leading-8","children":["The five strategies in this guide offer options for every budget and situation. Start with the approaches that fit your current setup, measure your results, and expand from there."]}]
